"...The TFLN platform incorporates topological photonic crystals to create protected edge-state waveguides. These structures provide backscattering-immune light propagation that is inherently robust against defects and disorder (as demonstrated in topological photonics literature). This physical-layer protection complements the system-level topological surplus generated via Artin braid inversion, resulting in multi-layered resilience.""}}}, "rest_id": "2074555776899719638", "source": "<a href="http://twitter.com/download/android" rel="nofollow">Twitter for Android</a>", "unmention_data": {}, "views": {"count": "16", "state": "EnabledWithCount"}}

